sequenceDiagram
    participant M as RocketMQ
    participant C1 as Consumer-1
    participant P as PostgreSQL
    participant C2 as Consumer-2

    M->>C1: 投递 message_id=M1
    C1->>P: BEGIN
    C1->>P: Inbox + 库存 + 订单 + 流水
    C1->>P: COMMIT
    P-->>C1: 成功

    C1--xM: ACK 前宕机

    M->>C2: 重投 message_id=M1
    C2->>P: INSERT Inbox ON CONFLICT
    P-->>C2: affected rows=0
    C2->>M: ACK
